Package model.hand.analyzer Description

This package contains the representation for HandAnalyzer interface, abstract class, and its implementations.

The package contains information about how to compare player's hands to each other, and implementations of the class to do the comparing. The package is necessary for determining the winner of a hand. This package contains part of the Model of MVC representation used throughout.
